sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Runtime as Runtime .NET
    participant DI as DI (static)
    participant Builder as ConfigurationBuilder
    participant Files as appsettings.json
    participant SC as ServiceCollection
    participant Provider as IServiceProvider

    Runtime->>DI: premier accès à la classe
    activate DI

    DI->>SC: new ServiceCollection()
    DI->>Builder: new ConfigurationBuilder()
    DI->>Files: AddJsonFile(appsettings.json)
    DI->>Files: AddJsonFile(appsettings-local.json)
    DI->>Builder: Build()
    Builder-->>DI: IConfiguration

    DI->>SC: AddSingleton SensorsConfig (depuis section sensorsConfig)
    DI->>SC: AddSingleton IConfiguration
    DI->>SC: AddKeyedSingleton IConfiguration (local, global)

    DI->>SC: BuildServiceProvider()
    SC-->>DI: _provider

    DI->>Provider: GetService IConfiguration (warm-up)
    deactivate DI

    Note over Runtime,Provider: DI.Provider disponible pour RandomAsyncSensorFactory
